/*
 * HapticCandlestick.cpp
 * =====================
 * Drop into an existing CHAI3D GLFW example project (replace its .cpp).
 *
 * Chart behaviour:
 *   - Exactly 50 packet slots always visible (static window width)
 *   - Newest packet at the RIGHT, oldest at the LEFT  (scrolls right→left)
 *   - Y axis is FIXED: 0 .. cfg::YMAX metres, never zooms or shifts
 *   - Middle reference line is STATIC at cfg::YMID
 *   - X axis shows real timestamps (seconds since start) under each slot
 *   - Instantaneous x, y, z values and magnitude shown in info panel
 *
 * Only extra linker dep vs a stock CHAI3D project:
 *   ws2_32.lib  (Winsock2 – already handled by #pragma comment below)
 *
 * Controls:  +/- step window | [ = 1ms max rate | ] = 1000ms min rate | N net | ESC quit
 */

